data.description: Desirable N. Tacoma Craftsman! 3,034 sq feet, 4 beds/ 3 Baths. Timeless charm & character in very sought-after location. Open main level w/ hardwood floors, fireplace, updated kitchen plus covered porch & back deck. Upper level consists of a sizable Primary Suite w/ dormered ceiling. Laundry hookups on main & lower levels. Basement has extensive updates- has interior & exterior entrance. Could use as MIL or rentable space- even has its own walk-out Trex deck w/ integrated lighting. Basement upgrades include: flooring, electrical & plumbing, workshop space w/ 240V outlets. Ready for 2nd kitchen w/ wtr, pwr & gas installed. Newer roof, gutters, paint, fence & retaining wall. Walking distance to UPS, Proctor, restaurants on I St & 6th Ave!
